00:11:52.305 --> 00:11:57.070
un dernokh hot men mir gezogt az s'iz tsvekloz, nishto derfun.

00:11:55.967 --> 00:12:00.010
vos iz forgekumen mit ayer mishpokhe, mit ayere eltern?

00:11:59.187 --> 00:12:01.150
alemen hot men tseharget.

00:12:00.709 --> 00:12:02.660
zey ⟨zaynen antlofn⟩ fun Varshe vuhin?

00:12:02.187 --> 00:12:05.170
zey zaynen antlofn keyn, fun Varshe keyn Baranovitsh.

00:12:05.228 --> 00:12:08.415
fun Baranovitsh zaynen zey antlofn in dem shtetl Mir.

00:12:08.623 --> 00:12:10.696
in dem shtetl Mir

00:12:10.696 --> 00:12:14.786
vayle dortn iz geven oyslendishe a sakh bokherim, hot men gemeynt

00:12:14.786 --> 00:12:16.886
az me vet nisht tshepen dem shtetl

00:12:16.886 --> 00:12:18.596
zaynen ale gelofn ahin.

00:12:18.664 --> 00:12:20.150
un dortn

00:12:20.150 --> 00:12:23.956
hot men zey alemen tsunoyfgeklibn, un m'hot zey umgebrakht.

00:12:24.570 --> 00:12:26.386
fun vanet veyst ir vegn dem?

00:12:26.832 --> 00:12:29.138
ikh bin dokh nokh der milkhome geven dort

00:12:29.464 --> 00:12:33.744
hob ikh getrofn mer nisht tsvey mentshn velkhe zaynen lebn geblibn.

00:12:34.290 --> 00:12:38.098
dos iz geven GARKAVI eyner

00:12:38.442 --> 00:12:41.406
un dokter ⟨Miler's⟩ a tokhter

00:12:42.812 --> 00:12:44.915
ir hot zey gekent far der milkhome?

00:12:44.972 --> 00:12:48.622
ikh, neyn. ⟨Miler's⟩ ba- GA- GARKAVIn hob ikh gekent

00:12:48.622 --> 00:12:51.142
un ⟨Miler's⟩ tokhter hob ikh nisht gekent.

00:12:51.503 --> 00:12:54.737
az ikh bin gekumen hob ikh zey getrofn, un zey hobn mir alts dertseylt.

00:12:55.165 --> 00:12:58.382
vi azoy s'iz forgekumen, un vos iz zey forgekumen

00:12:58.590 --> 00:13:01.537
vi me hot reb Shayen

00:13:01.847 --> 00:13:02.820
geharget.

00:13:02.978 --> 00:13:04.305
ver iz reb Shaye gevezn?

00:13:04.316 --> 00:13:09.030
nu, der heyliker yid velkher di poylishe poyerim hobn nisht gelozn

00:13:09.222 --> 00:13:11.005
az me zol im hargenen.

00:13:14.483 --> 00:13:16.027
er iz geven a heyliker.

00:13:15.870 --> 00:13:18.446
ir hot z- ir zayt geblibn

00:13:18.486 --> 00:13:22.108
nokh dem shpitol zayt ir avekgegangen, zayt ir geblibn lebn vu?

00:13:22.266 --> 00:13:23.576
in Babroysk.

00:13:24.679 --> 00:13:26.073
vos ⟨hot men⟩ dortn geton?

00:13:26.603 --> 00:13:29.516
nu, bin ikh dokh avek tsun im in kolkhoz.

00:13:30.552 --> 00:13:36.165
er hot dokh mir tsugenumen. ikh hob dokh im ge- geratevet. ikh fleg im

00:13:36.205 --> 00:13:40.380
tsugebn ah esn epes un trinken epes, biz vanen er

00:13:39.715 --> 00:13:40.755
vu iz dos gevezn?

00:13:40.859 --> 00:13:42.499
in Babroysk in shpitol

00:13:42.972 --> 00:13:44.940
in shpitol ⟨ven m'hot im⟩ gebrakht.

00:13:44.085 --> 00:13:46.306
vi iz e- vi iz er ahingekumen

00:13:46.633 --> 00:13:48.281
gekumen tsum shpitol?

00:13:48.220 --> 00:13:49.776
tsum shpitol?

00:13:49.776 --> 00:13:54.876
vayle er iz dokh geven a firer in der armey, vu s'hot getrofn a bombe aropgefaln

00:13:54.876 --> 00:13:56.246
oyf zayn CAR

00:13:56.607 --> 00:13:58.491
un hot im opgerisn a hant

00:13:58.581 --> 00:14:02.543
di rekhte hant im opgerisn. er iz geven in gantsn a farvundeter.

00:14:02.547 --> 00:14:04.397
ir hot i- ir hot im gehelfn?

00:14:04.383 --> 00:14:06.236
ikh hob im geholfn, vayle

00:14:06.259 --> 00:14:09.820
me hot dokh nisht gekukt demolt. me flegt dort brengen hunderter

00:14:09.820 --> 00:14:11.420
iz ver hot oyf zey gekukt?

00:14:11.420 --> 00:14:13.644
geshtorbn, geshtorbn. vemes dayge iz es?

00:14:13.819 --> 00:14:16.566
un ⟨dem⟩ hot ⟨opgebrakht⟩, un er hot di

00:14:16.566 --> 00:14:17.984
flegt er

00:14:17.984 --> 00:14:23.280
krekhtsn un betn a bisl vaser, betn vos es iz, iz keyner hot oyf im nit gekukt

00:14:23.280 --> 00:14:27.520
hob ikh, un ikh hob shoyn gekent arumgeyn, fleg ikh tsugeyn im gebn a bisele vaser

00:14:27.520 --> 00:14:32.241
im gebn a bisele sup. vos tsu esn iz dort shoyn geven in shpitol, hot ⟨men nor⟩ gegebn esn.

00:14:32.719 --> 00:14:34.822
es iz nisht geven ver es zol gebn

00:14:38.153 --> 00:14:41.134
vayter vos i- vos hot ir geton dortn in dem

00:14:38.187 --> 00:14:39.430
nu

00:14:41.120 --> 00:14:42.110
in kolkho-

00:14:41.832 --> 00:14:42.585
ye.

00:14:42.574 --> 00:14:45.018
nu, vayter, az er iz ge-

00:14:45.018 --> 00:14:47.538
az er iz gekumen tsu der makht

00:14:47.873 --> 00:14:50.932
ORLOVSKY iz dokh gekumen tsu der makht. STALIN hot im

00:14:50.932 --> 00:14:55.190
tsugenumen, im gegebn ale meglekhkeytn er zol oyfboyen dem kolkhoz

00:14:55.787 --> 00:14:57.755
hot er genumen mir zukhn

00:14:58.420 --> 00:15:02.565
un er iz f- un er hot mir gezukht azoy lang biz vanen er hot mir gefunen.

00:15:02.740 --> 00:15:06.919
er hot mir gefunen, hot er mir tsugenumen tsu im vayl ikh zol zayn zayn fartreter.

00:15:07.960 --> 00:15:08.650
shoyn.

00:15:09.388 --> 00:15:11.424
mit vos ⟨iz zikh⟩ dortn farnumen?

00:15:09.422 --> 00:15:10.450
un

00:15:11.616 --> 00:15:13.820
mir ba- baarbetn di erd

00:15:15.143 --> 00:15:16.930
dort iz geven.

00:15:15.767 --> 00:15:18.174
vi a fartreter, vos hot ir, vos UNK geton?

00:15:17.497 --> 00:15:20.867
ah, vi a fartreter vos iz geven mayn arbet?

00:15:20.867 --> 00:15:22.463
ikh fleg UNK

00:15:22.463 --> 00:15:26.066
farnemen zikh mit firn in

00:15:26.066 --> 00:15:30.589
di frukhtn, geven ⟨zeyer groy-⟩ firn frukhtn in farsheydene

00:15:30.589 --> 00:15:35.640
in KUYBYSHEV, in avu s'iz geven tayer, vu me flegt kenen nemen a sakh gelt

00:15:35.730 --> 00:15:37.093
hob ikh ⟨geton⟩

00:15:37.093 --> 00:15:39.200
nu, ikh hob alts geton.

00:15:39.207 --> 00:15:40.807
alts vos i-

00:15:40.807 --> 00:15:42.401
vos darf ton a

00:15:42.401 --> 00:15:43.352
a firer.

00:15:44.218 --> 00:15:46.861
ir hot gelebt in shtot Babroysk?

00:15:46.220 --> 00:15:50.136
in shtot Babroysk, yo. un er hot mir oysgeboyt a sheyne hoyz

00:15:50.665 --> 00:15:51.975
a groyse

00:15:53.061 --> 00:15:55.147
un gegebn a groysn gehalt

00:15:55.339 --> 00:15:56.154
un shoyn.

00:15:56.132 --> 00:15:57.779
ir hot khasene gehat?

00:15:57.690 --> 00:15:58.691
yo.

00:15:58.765 --> 00:15:59.766
vi azoy?

00:15:59.766 --> 00:16:01.408
vi hot ir getrofn ayer froy?

00:16:01.684 --> 00:16:02.943
in Babroysk.

00:16:03.085 --> 00:16:07.719
hobn mir bakant un ikh bin geven a bokher, zi iz geven a meydl, mir hobn khasene gehat.

00:16:10.813 --> 00:16:12.376
bay aykh zaynen do kinder?

00:16:12.535 --> 00:16:13.322
avu?

00:16:13.986 --> 00:16:15.228
mit ayer froy?

00:16:15.319 --> 00:16:18.013
yo. nu, der zun mit der

00:16:18.171 --> 00:16:19.633
mit der tokhter.

00:16:18.400 --> 00:16:19.583
vifl kinder hot ir?

00:16:19.808 --> 00:16:20.831
tsvey.

00:16:21.090 --> 00:16:22.771
dem zun mit der tokhter.

00:16:23.908 --> 00:16:25.370
nokh der milkhome

00:16:25.680 --> 00:16:27.868
az ir zayt shoyn gevezn in Babroysk

00:16:28.212 --> 00:16:31.361
iz gevezn a tsayt vos

00:16:31.603 --> 00:16:35.954
s'iz gevezn di antisemitizm groys? aykh vi a yid hot men epes

00:16:35.954 --> 00:16:37.144
hot ir zikh gefilt

00:16:37.144 --> 00:16:38.266
az UNK

00:16:38.266 --> 00:16:39.579
ni- nit keyn

00:16:39.636 --> 00:16:41.807
ful- fuler mentsh, vi

00:16:42.808 --> 00:16:44.290
es iz geven

00:16:44.290 --> 00:16:45.570
eyn fal.

00:16:46.065 --> 00:16:48.809
az ikh bin eyn mol gegangen farbay

00:16:49.137 --> 00:16:52.877
s'iz geven friling, velkhe m'hot gedarft zeyen di felder

00:16:53.035 --> 00:16:55.782
un ikh ze vi es shteyt a CAR

00:16:55.782 --> 00:16:58.007
undzere vos darf firn dem

00:16:59.076 --> 00:17:01.519
nu vi ruft zikh UNK

00:17:01.519 --> 00:17:03.221
vos baarbet di erd, nu?

00:17:03.430 --> 00:17:07.963
darf firn, iz di mentshn zitsn un me est, tsen mentshn.

00:17:08.509 --> 00:17:10.173
zog ikh tsu zey

00:17:10.213 --> 00:17:14.243
"far vos darf epes tsen mentshn zitsn un der CAR darf shteyn?

00:17:14.243 --> 00:17:17.517
s'iz dokh friling. me darf dokh zeyen. s'iz a shod di tsayt.

00:17:17.517 --> 00:17:20.905
zoln finf UNK esn, un ⟨finfe⟩ zoln arbetn

00:17:21.317 --> 00:17:23.066
un der CAR zol nit shteyn."

00:17:23.426 --> 00:17:29.310
hot zikh oyfgehoybn eyner un gezogt "ZHIDOVSKAYA MORDA, gey avek, vayle ikh vel dir bald tseteytn."

00:17:29.991 --> 00:17:31.639
hob ikh zikh oysgeton

00:17:32.050 --> 00:17:35.480
un ikh hob genumen, mit mir iz gegangen der

00:17:35.480 --> 00:17:36.910
der AGRONOM

00:17:37.298 --> 00:17:40.720
a hoypt AGRONOM, ikh hob ge- un mir zalbe tsveyt hobn onge-

00:17:40.720 --> 00:17:42.948
ongelodn di mashin un avekgeshikt.

00:17:42.948 --> 00:17:45.960
ikh hob zikh nisht far ORLOVSKYn nisht baklogt

00:17:45.960 --> 00:17:47.149
far dem, UNK

00:17:47.149 --> 00:17:49.374
nor ikh veyst az er hot zikh dervust fun dem.

00:17:49.667 --> 00:17:52.192
oyf morgn in der fri hot er gemakht a

00:17:52.603 --> 00:17:55.410
farzamlung fun dem gantsn kolkhoz

00:17:55.410 --> 00:17:59.474
un hot aroysgerufn der vos hot oyf mir gezogt ZHYDOVSKAYA MORDA

00:17:59.742 --> 00:18:03.229
"iz zog, vu hostu gezogt oyf undzer FEDYA?"

00:18:03.640 --> 00:18:04.944
zogt er "kh'hob gornit ge-"

00:18:04.944 --> 00:18:07.274
"zog vi hostu gezogt far FEDYA

00:18:07.274 --> 00:18:08.240
oyf FEDYA."

00:18:08.331 --> 00:18:12.437
nu, hobn a- di andere gezogt az er hot gezogt ZHYDOVSKAYA MORDA.

00:18:12.437 --> 00:18:14.720
"morgn biz tsvelf a zeyger

00:18:14.727 --> 00:18:16.956
zolstu ⟨do⟩ nisht zayn in kolkhoz

00:18:16.956 --> 00:18:20.516
nisht du, nisht dayne kinder, nisht dayn vayb, keyner nisht

00:18:20.516 --> 00:18:21.826
aroys fun ⟨der⟩

00:18:21.826 --> 00:18:23.090
aroys."

00:18:23.518 --> 00:18:25.334
ven iz dos gevezn? velkhn yor?

00:18:25.280 --> 00:18:28.772
dos iz geven, velkhn yor iz dos geven?

00:18:28.772 --> 00:18:32.372
in akht un fertsik. UNK ikh ⟨ongehoybn⟩ in fuftsiktn yor.

00:18:33.120 --> 00:18:36.067
gedenkt ir di geshikhte mit di yidishe doktoyrim

00:18:36.124 --> 00:18:38.666
vos iz forgekumen in Rusland demolt?

00:18:38.702 --> 00:18:41.014
ikh hob nisht

00:18:41.014 --> 00:18:43.503
ikh bin geven farnumen, un ikh hob nisht

00:18:43.503 --> 00:18:45.028
ts- aynteylgenumen.

00:18:45.220 --> 00:18:48.538
un ir hot gefilt epes yene tsayt? ir aleyn.

00:18:48.498 --> 00:18:49.477
b- ikh, neyn.

00:18:49.477 --> 00:18:52.486
bay undz in kolkhoz nokh dem

00:18:52.813 --> 00:18:57.293
vi es iz geshen dem tsufal vos er hot aroysgetribn dem kolkhoznik

00:18:57.293 --> 00:18:58.993
far dem vos er hot oyf mir gezogt

00:18:58.993 --> 00:19:02.213
flegt men keyn eyn shlekhtn vort hob ikh keyn mol nisht gehert.

00:19:02.230 --> 00:19:05.886
mer nit ikh hob gehert az ven es iz a yontev

00:19:06.094 --> 00:19:11.270
fleg ikh muzn antloyfn, vayle der hot gezogt "neyn, du vest kumen tsu mir esn," der hot gezogt

00:19:11.270 --> 00:19:13.970
"neyn, du vest kumen tsu mir, Khaim, esn un trinken"

00:19:13.970 --> 00:19:16.290
un

00:19:16.290 --> 00:19:17.563
kh'hob nisht gefilt gornisht.

00:19:18.193 --> 00:19:22.676
ir hot gelebt in Babroysk. iz geven a, a sakh yidn zaynen gevezn dortn?

00:19:23.796 --> 00:19:27.320
geven a kulturishe, a RELIGIOSEr lebn vos iz UNK

00:19:27.762 --> 00:19:31.150
ver es hot gevolt zikh firn RELIGIOS hot zikh gefirt RELIGIOS.

00:19:30.765 --> 00:19:32.126
gevezn a shul dortn?

00:19:31.984 --> 00:19:34.334
geve- a, keyn shul iz nit geven. a minyen.

00:19:35.153 --> 00:19:37.560
a minyen. bay mir in shtub geven a minyen.

00:19:38.443 --> 00:19:39.888
ver flegt UNK klaybn?

00:19:40.030 --> 00:19:40.786
vos?

00:19:40.772 --> 00:19:42.791
ver flegt zikh tsuzamenklaybn bay aykh?

00:19:42.770 --> 00:19:43.482
yidn.

00:19:44.063 --> 00:19:44.917
yidn.

00:19:45.126 --> 00:19:46.065
vi oft?

00:19:45.670 --> 00:19:48.430
zey hobn mir mer nisht gezogt eyn zakh. her zikh ayn.

00:19:48.430 --> 00:19:50.310
FEDYE, FEDYE, hobn zey mir gerufn.

00:19:50.310 --> 00:19:52.663
ikh bin geven mit zey mit alemen bakant.

00:19:52.939 --> 00:19:56.662
"az ir klaybt zikh oyf, zolt ir vegn politik nisht reydn.

00:19:56.753 --> 00:19:58.099
reydt vegn

00:19:58.099 --> 00:20:00.150
libe, reydt vegn der luft

00:20:00.150 --> 00:20:02.270
reydt vegn vos, nor nisht vegn politik.

00:20:02.270 --> 00:20:04.391
vet ir kenen oplebn toyznt yor."

00:20:04.785 --> 00:20:07.494
zog ikh "far vos az es kumen dokh b- eygene mentsh-"

00:20:07.494 --> 00:20:09.824
"oyber" zogt er "dray mentshn fun aykh

00:20:09.824 --> 00:20:11.824
reydn iz eyner undzerer."

00:20:13.037 --> 00:20:13.875
farshteyst?

00:20:13.982 --> 00:20:15.714
"un er vet glaykh derleygn."

00:20:16.260 --> 00:20:19.966
shoyn, az mir UNK mit politik zikh nisht farnumen.

00:20:20.023 --> 00:20:22.036
oyf yontoyvim flegt ir zikh klaybn

00:20:22.036 --> 00:20:24.185
tsuzamenklaybn? oyf yidishe yontoyvim.

00:20:23.160 --> 00:20:23.850
yo.

00:20:24.086 --> 00:20:24.846
yo.

00:20:24.846 --> 00:20:28.168
yo, flegn kumen tsu mir mayne fraynt. ikh fleg kumen tsu zey.

00:20:28.613 --> 00:20:31.014
ir flegt opmerkn di yidishe yontoyvim?

00:20:30.760 --> 00:20:31.390
?

00:20:31.014 --> 00:20:35.880
in ayer mishpokhe flegt ir opmerkn di yidishe yontoyvim? nokh der milkhome?

00:20:33.772 --> 00:20:36.682
yo, yo. yo.

00:20:37.000 --> 00:20:38.242
velkhe yontoyvim?

00:20:38.070 --> 00:20:40.380
peysekh, sukes

00:20:40.380 --> 00:20:42.390
rosheshone, yomkiper.

00:20:42.012 --> 00:20:44.621
ir flegt makhn a seyder oyf peysekh?

00:20:44.021 --> 00:20:45.571
y- UNK

00:20:46.062 --> 00:20:49.144
UNK makhn a seyder un zingen a gantse nakht

00:20:50.365 --> 00:20:54.864
nu, UNK mayn zun hot men gemave- gemalet, geven a bris

00:20:55.073 --> 00:20:57.837
un s'iz geven ofn di fentster, un s'iz geven

00:20:57.837 --> 00:21:00.804
a khasene hob ikh gemakht f- mit, mitn rov

00:21:01.401 --> 00:21:02.984
vi, vi es darf tsu zayn.

00:21:02.937 --> 00:21:05.681
m'hot aykh nit aroysgetribn fun der arbet derfar?

00:21:05.788 --> 00:21:06.524
neyn.

00:21:06.835 --> 00:21:08.820
ir ⟨zayt⟩ gevezn a komunist? neyn?

00:21:08.460 --> 00:21:09.107
neyn.

00:21:09.315 --> 00:21:14.051
er hot toyznt mol mir gezogt "Khaim, gey in der partye," hob ikh gezogt "neyn."

00:21:17.365 --> 00:21:22.286
er hot shoyn aleyn derfilt az UNK dos iz nisht, nisht dos

00:21:22.562 --> 00:21:25.171
iz az er flegt zayn in a gute shtimung

00:21:25.330 --> 00:21:27.450
flegt er tsu mir zogn "FEDKE

00:21:27.912 --> 00:21:29.222
s'iz nisht dos.

00:21:29.903 --> 00:21:33.930
s'iz nit ⟨dos⟩" zogt er. "nisht far dem hob ikh opgegebn mayne hent un fis."

00:21:35.995 --> 00:21:40.640
in Babroysk bay aykh gevezn, flegt ir bakumen yidishe tsaytungen

00:21:40.640 --> 00:21:43.751
nokh di milkhome ⟨heyst⟩ UNK. bikher zaynen gevezn bay aykh?

00:21:41.690 --> 00:21:43.450
nu, in Babroysk iz

00:21:43.450 --> 00:21:45.190
geven, vi ⟨iz⟩ UNK

00:21:43.960 --> 00:21:47.120
s'iz gevezn a yidisher teater? artistn flegn

00:21:45.970 --> 00:21:48.480
geven, geven, geven, geven.

00:21:47.672 --> 00:21:49.963
ir gedenkt velkhe nit iz fun zey?

00:21:50.811 --> 00:21:55.020
teater iz geven nit keyn shtendiker, di vos flegn kumen UNK mer nisht.

00:21:53.798 --> 00:21:56.340
gedenkt ir di artistn vos flegn kumen?

00:21:55.450 --> 00:21:57.284
Mikhoels flegt kumen.

00:21:57.780 --> 00:22:00.553
Mikhoels flegt kumen, un

00:22:00.553 --> 00:22:03.714
ANNA GUZIK flegt kumen zeyer oft.

00:22:04.716 --> 00:22:06.380
 nu

00:22:07.045 --> 00:22:08.338
iz di

00:22:08.715 --> 00:22:13.141
un aleyn zaynen geven libhober velkhe hobn geshtelt yidishe

00:22:13.141 --> 00:22:14.497
forshtelungen.

00:22:18.283 --> 00:22:21.618
ir hot bakumen yidishe tsaytungen oder zhurnaln? neyn?

00:22:21.500 --> 00:22:23.317
UNK geven ⟨nokh⟩.

00:22:23.228 --> 00:22:25.820
in ayer shtub ikh meyn, in ayer mishpokhe.

